-- Fairfax May Hold Wells Fargo, US Bank for Another 5-to-10 Years
-- B y   S e a n   B .   P a s t e r n a k
-- 2012-04-26T14:40:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-26/fairfax-may-hold-wells-fargo-us-bank-for-another-5-to-10-years.html
Fairfax Financial Holdings Ltd. (FFH)  may
hold investments in Wells Fargo,  US Bancorp (USB)  and  Johnson &
Johnson (JNJ)  for the next “five to 10 years,” Chief Executive
Officer  Prem Watsa  said.  “Their earnings could double,” Watsa said at Fairfax’s
annual meeting of shareholders in Toronto.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sean B. Pasternak in Toronto at 
 spasternak@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
